A '''hind limb''' is a [[posterior]] [[limb]] on an [[animal]].  When referring to [[quadruped]]s, the term '''hind leg''' is often instead used. Hind limb is used for locomotion like walking, moving and running. Without a limb the inability to move will become a factor.
